'''Death Star Troopers''' were elite [[Imperial Navy Trooper]]s stationed aboard both the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station|first]] and [[DS-2 Death Star II Mobile Battle Station|second Death Star]]. They [[pilot]]ed the [[battle station]]s to their destinations, guarded prisoners, and also fired the [[superlaser]] aboard each,<ref name="Death Star Troopers" /> along with [[Imperial weapons technician]]s.<ref name="Episode IV">{{Film|IV}}</ref> They maintained [[Death Star trooper officer corps|their own]] [[officer corps]], which consisted of [[trooper]]s who had been trained in leadership and administration along with standard Death Star Trooper training.<ref name="Dawn" /> Individuals who served as Death Star Troopers included [[Corporal]] [[Ansin Thobel]]<ref name="SWROUVG">''[[Star Wars: Rogue One: The Ultimate Visual Guide]]''</ref> and [[Jad Bean]].<ref name="Episode VI" />

